        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="audit" value="audit [tail] [root] [--limit count]&lt;br&gt;AuditCommand reads .agent/audit/events.ndjson&lt;br&gt;Prints recent event metadata" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#E6FFFA;strokeColor=#2C7A7B;fontSize=12" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="350" y="525" width="270" height="95" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="run" value="run&lt;br&gt;RunCommand parses options&lt;br&gt;AgentRuntimeFactory creates LlmInferenceClient + ConversationRuntimeState + DefaultConversationLoopRunner&lt;br&gt;Loads default loop definition + system-locked graph&lt;br&gt;Runtime surface = cli" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#E9D8FD;strokeColor=#6B46C1;fontSize=13;fontStyle=1" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="350" y="670" width="270" height="100" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="banner" value="Cli.Command.AgentRuntimeConsoleHost.RunAsync(...)&lt;br&gt;Print banner&lt;br&gt;Own console input/output only" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FAF5FF;strokeColor=#6B46C1;fontSize=12" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="700" y="645" width="230" height="75" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="options" value="LlmInferenceClientOptions&lt;br&gt;Surface = OpenAiCodex&lt;br&gt;model from --model / -m / positional or Web options&lt;br&gt;workdir from --workdir or current dir&lt;br&gt;codex path and sandbox" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FAF5FF;strokeColor=#6B46C1;fontSize=12" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="995" y="620" width="275" height="135" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="prompt" value="Loop until exit&lt;br&gt;Console writes User: prompt&lt;br&gt;Console.ReadLine() then AgentRuntime.RunTurnAsync(...)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FAF5FF;strokeColor=#6B46C1;fontSize=12" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="700" y="785" width="230" height="85" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="exitDecision" value="EOF or exit command?&lt;br&gt;/exit, /quit, exit, quit" style="rhombus;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFF7E6;strokeColor=#B7791F;fontSize=12" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="995" y="785" width="165" height="110" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="return0" value="Return 0" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#F0FFF4;strokeColor=#2F855A;fontSize=12;fontStyle=1" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1225" y="805" width="130" height="50" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="blankDecision" value="blank input?" style="rhombus;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFF7E6;strokeColor=#B7791F;fontSize=12" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="700" y="920" width="135" height="90" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="addUser" value="DefaultConversationLoopRunner.RunTurnAsync(input)&lt;br&gt;Acquire cross-process, workspace-scoped conversation lease before context assembly&lt;br&gt;Synchronize runtime transcript from durable current conversation&lt;br&gt;Create + validate run, append user state + memory&lt;br&gt;Hold lease across inference and assistant state + memory persistence" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#EBF8FF;strokeColor=#3182CE;fontSize=12" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="930" y="920" width="245" height="90" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="generate" value="LlmInferenceClient.GenerateAsync(request)&lt;br&gt;Delegates through audited provider pipeline&lt;br&gt;Append llm.inference.start if .agent exists" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#EBF8FF;strokeColor=#3182CE;fontSize=12" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1240" y="920" width="285" height="95" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="surface" value="Internal provider factory&lt;br&gt;Surface switch" style="rhombus;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFF7E6;strokeColor=#B7791F;fontSize=12" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1268" y="1055" width="145" height="90" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="unsupported" value="Azure AI Foundry / other surfaces&lt;br&gt;NotSupportedInferenceClient&lt;br&gt;Currently placeholder only" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFF5F5;strokeColor=#C53030;fontSize=12" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1040" y="1070" width="205" height="80" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="codex" value="CodexAppServerInferenceClient&lt;br&gt;ContextBuilder builds turn input + assigned command guidance&lt;br&gt;ToolBridge exposes loop-assigned dynamic commands" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#EBF8FF;strokeColor=#3182CE;fontSize=12" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1240" y="1185" width="285" height="85" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="process" value="Start Codex app-server process&lt;br&gt;codex[.cmd] app-server --stdio&lt;br&gt;Send JSON-RPC thread/start + turn/start&lt;br&gt;Read item/agentMessage/delta + turn/completed" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#EBF8FF;strokeColor=#3182CE;fontSize=12" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1240" y="1310" width="285" height="125" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="exitCode" value="turn/completed status?" style="rhombus;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFF7E6;strokeColor=#B7791F;fontSize=12" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1265" y="1475" width="170" height="95" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="failure" value="Failure path&lt;br&gt;Record failed/cancelled loop run&lt;br&gt;Return AgentRuntimeTurnResult failure/cancelled&lt;br&gt;Surface projects error/cancel event" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFF5F5;strokeColor=#C53030;fontSize=12" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="960" y="1470" width="250" height="115" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="success" value="Success path&lt;br&gt;Extract final agentMessage from turn/completed&lt;br&gt;Return LlmInferenceResponse&lt;br&gt;Append llm.inference.complete succeeded if audit log exists" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#F0FFF4;strokeColor=#2F855A;fontSize=12" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1240" y="1610" width="285" height="95" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="print" value="DefaultConversationLoopRunner stores assistant output while lease remains held&lt;br&gt;Record completed loop run or surface terminal persistence failure&lt;br&gt;Release workspace conversation lease&lt;br&gt;Console/Web projects output; prompt again" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#F0FFF4;strokeColor=#2F855A;fontSize=12" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="930" y="1630" width="240" height="80" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="boundaries" value="Current boundaries&lt;br&gt;- Default conversation turns flow through DefaultConversationLoopRunner and AgentRuntime.RunTurnAsync.&lt;br&gt;- Workspace bootstrap treats AGENTS.md + .agent/ROLE.md as contextual role instructions, SOUL.md + PERSONALITY.md as durable agent identity, and CONTEXT.md + MEMORY.md + models.json as lower-authority state; old AGENT.md workspaces require reinitialization.&lt;br&gt;- One file-backed workspace conversation lease serializes default turns across runtime instances and processes from durable transcript synchronization through inference and assistant state + memory persistence.&lt;br&gt;- The default definition remains a system-locked graph loaded from .agent/loops/definitions when present.&lt;br&gt;- Default-turn run records cover started/completed/failed/cancelled outcomes; terminal persistence failure surfaces as a failed turn.&lt;br&gt;- Loop CapabilityIds filter workspace commands before ToolPermissionService + ToolBroker enforce path policy, approval, execution, full-response retention, and audit.&lt;br&gt;- Complete bounded tool responses are chunked under .agent/logs/tool-responses before 64,000-character model formatting; references/hashes remain visible and inspection requires approval.&lt;br&gt;- Web and CLI project the same default-conversation semantics.&lt;br&gt;- Custom authoring/execution uses a separate Startup facade and ordered runtime shown on the Custom Loop MVP page.&lt;br&gt;- Both paths share AgentRuntime and logical ConversationRuntimeState only for explicitly captured or published product context.&lt;br&gt;- Each custom attempt owns a fresh provider transport and run-scoped ToolBroker; the custom execution gate does not globally serialize ordinary chat." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#F7FAFC;strokeColor=#718096;fontSize=12;dashed=1" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="70" y="870" width="520" height="300" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="maintenance" value="Documentation maintenance&lt;br&gt;Agents should update README.md and this draw.io source in the same change when real implementation behavior changes." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFFAF0;strokeColor=#C05621;fontSize=12;dashed=1" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="70" y="1155" width="520" height="85" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
